---

<BaseLayout
  title="Workshops"
  description="Meet our dedicated church staff and leadership team who serve our congregation with passion and commitment."
>
  <PageHeader 
    title="Workshops" 
    subtitle="Tailored to your Organisation or Group"
    backgroundImage="/uploads/workshops-header.jpg"
    overlayOpacity={0.35}
  />
  
  
  <!-- About Me/Ariane -->
   <!-- add diversity and inclusion and intercultural communication in future-->
  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container">
      <!--
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">What We Believe</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our church adheres to these fundamental Christian beliefs
        </p>
      </div>
      -->

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto prose prose-lg">

        <p>
            I offer workshops for universities, teams, and organisations on a range of topics related to <b>productivity, executive functioning, stress management, and change</b>.
            All workshops are <b>designed collaboratively</b> so they fully match the needs of your audience.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
          <div>
            <h3 class="blueFont">Example Workshop Themes</h3>
            <p>
              <ul class="green-bullets">
                <li>Managing stress and overwhelm</li>
                <li>Breaking procrastination</li>
                <li>Habit change that lasts</li>
                <li>Introduction to the change cycle</li>
                <li>Career clarity sessions (e.g., Ikigai-based workshop)</li>
                <li>Creating inclusive learning or working environments</li>
                <li>Talks on patterns, mindset, and practical change</li>
              </ul>
            </p>
          </div>
        
          <div>
            <h3 class="blueFont">Formats Types</h3>
